                                <h2 class="text-10 text-dark">Accreditation For Food Safety Management Systems (FSMS)
                                </h2>
                                <p class="text-dark text-dark text-4">
                                    Food Safety Management Systems certification is provided by certification bodies to
                                    organizations who have demonstrated that they have implemented a system for food
                                    safety along the food chain. ISO 22000 specifies requirements for a food safety
                                    management system that combines interactive communication, system management,
                                    prerequisite program, and HACCP principles to ensure food safety along the food
                                    chain. <br>
                                    <br>
                                    A Certification Body applying for ISO 22000 accreditation must conform to ISO/IEC
                                    17021, ISO/TS 22003 and other additional International requirements as detailed in
                                    Specific Requirements for Accreditation for FSMS Scheme.<br>
                                    <br>
                                    Certification Bodies interested to apply for an Accreditation scheme for FSMS can
                                    send an email at <a href="mailto:usacamerica@gmail.com "> usacamerica@gmail.com </a> demanding for following Application
                                    documents.
                                    <br>
                                    <br>
                                <ol class="text-dark text-dark text-4">
                                    <li>Accreditation Application for Medical Devices Quality Management System:
                                        USAC-APL-CAB-MDQMS</li>
                                    <li>General Criteria for Accreditation Requirements: USAC-GEN-CAB-01</li>
                                    <li>General Criteria for Conditions for the Use of USAC Accreditation Symbol:
                                        USAC-GEN-CAB-02</li>
                                    <li>Accreditation Requirements for Medical Devices Quality Management
                                        System:USAC-CAB-MDQMS</li>
                                    <li>Applicable Fees: USAC-CAB-MS-FEES</li>
                                    <li>Documentation Checklist as per ISO/IEC 17021-1 and IAF MD9</li>
                                </ol>

